<h2>Amy Longo</h2>
<h4>Senior Account Executive</h4>
<h4>&nbsp;</h4>
<p>Amy is a Senior Account Executive at Wachsman PR.</p>
<p>Amy&rsquo;s specialties are media relations, analyst relations, copywriting, and social media management.</p>
<p>Originally from Australia, Amy started her career as a Communications and Marketing Manager at a Sydney-based IT consultancy. She then moved agency-side, joining Recognition PR as a Senior Account Executive, working alongside B2B enterprise technology and financial services clients including CenturyLink, Palo Alto Networks, and Atradius.</p>
<p>In January 2017, Amy moved to New York to join the team at Wachsman PR and has made an immediate impact. Amy holds a Master of Arts in Communications Management, a Bachelor of Arts in Communications (Journalism), and a Bachelor of Arts in International Studies (Italian) from the University of Technology, Sydney. She is interested in travel and technology.</p>